==Dharka==
[[File:Karachi_-_Pakistan-market.jpg|thumb|Suuq dharka lagu iibiyo oo ku yaala Karachi, Bakistaan.]]
'''[[Dhar]]ka''' ({{lang-en|Textile ama Cloth}}; {{lang-ar|نسيج (قماش)}}) waa shay dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]] la xardhay. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah. Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta. 
==Hordhac==
[[File:DumbartonOaksTextileEuropa.jpg|thumb|Cow ama sijaayad la isticmaali jirey wakhtigii faraaciyiinta dalka [[Masar]].]]
God ku yaala galbeedka wadanka Joorjiya ee bariga [[Yurub]] ayaa waxa laga helay qidcad harag oo lagu wado in dhar ahaan loo isticmaali jirey wakhti hada laga joogo 34,000 oo sano. Dharka guud ahaan waxaa la isku yidhaahdaa '''Hu<nowiki>'</nowiki>'''; kaasi oo u kala baxa noocyo badan. Kugu ugu muhiimsan ee dadku isticmaalaan maalin kasta waxaa ka mid ah: [[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]] iyo kuwo kale oo badan.<ref>''"[[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]]"''</ref>
